  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/e8b4f4a34500a1c4848f0152657710d0.avif?t=1737968851\" width=488 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Le Château</strong> (French for \"<i>the castle</i>\") is a tiny city builder, mostly about showing creativity with limited resources and limited space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for when you've got little to no time, but you have this itch to play a game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=598 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your kingdom as small as 1 tile, or as big as 11x11 tiles, and enjoy the aesthetics of several different color palettes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/434ea26975b2f7cee9745bfd262d82a8.avif?t=1737968851\" width=488 height=82 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⬜Multiple world shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🏰Dozens of different types of objects to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🎨6 different color palettes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 👑Complete control over the size of your kingdom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🤼A world that slowly comes alive as more tiles are filled</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🐸Frogs</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Le Château has no real goal. Just lots of freedom in building the kingdom of your dreams!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Paul Schnepf's The Block</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/e8b4f4a34500a1c4848f0152657710d0.avif?t=1737968851\" width=488 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Le Château</strong> (French for \"<i>the castle</i>\") is a tiny city builder, mostly about showing creativity with limited resources and limited space.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Great for when you've got little to no time, but you have this itch to play a game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=598 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/014fc5a57f2f7aa6f048ff6946df9ad0.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make your kingdom as small as 1 tile, or as big as 11x11 tiles, and enjoy the aesthetics of several different color palettes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.poster.avif?t=1737968851\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.webm?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/ba7bc4966da859267463483a7aa6afb8.mp4?t=1737968851\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2365980/extras/434ea26975b2f7cee9745bfd262d82a8.avif?t=1737968851\" width=488 height=82 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > ⬜Multiple world shapes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🏰Dozens of different types of objects to choose from</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🎨6 different color palettes</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 👑Complete control over the size of your kingdom</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🤼A world that slowly comes alive as more tiles are filled</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 🐸Frogs</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Le Château has no real goal. Just lots of freedom in building the kingdom of your dreams!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Inspired by Paul Schnepf's The Block</p>",
